## Follow NC Digital on Facebook, Instagram & X

We're now officially live on social media! At [NC Digital](/), we've been working hard behind the scenes helping local businesses across South Wales build fast, SEO-ready websites. Now, we're sharing that journey directly through Facebook, Instagram, and X (twitter).

Whether you're a local business owner, tradesperson, startup, or creative, we're here to give you web advice, practical tips, and a closer look at how we work. **Our goal is simple:** make it easier for small businesses to understand and succeed online — and have some fun doing it.

> "Being part of the local business scene means more than just working in it — it means connecting, sharing, and supporting each other every day."
> NC Digital

#### Why We're Going Social

As a small but growing agency based in Merthyr Tydfil, we understand the power of visibility. That's why we focus on SEO, clean web builds, and now — direct communication through social media. **By following us,** you'll gain access to quick tips, examples of local success, and free resources designed to help your business grow.

Plus, if we've worked with you or will soon — your project might be featured! It's a great way to boost your reach too.

#### Here's Where to Follow Us

- Facebook: [facebook.com/ncdigitaluk](https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=61575891781927)
- Instagram: [instagram.com/ncdigitaluk](https://www.instagram.com/ncdigitaluk/)
- X (Twitter): [x.com/ncdigitaluk](https://x.com/ncdigitaluk)

#### What We'll Be Posting

Our feeds won't be just ads or promotions. Instead, we'll share:

- Tips for building better websites and improving local SEO
- Client project launches and success stories
- Insights into tools we use, like WordPress, Elementor, and Rank Math
- Quick how-to advice for content, hosting, domains and more

**In addition,** we'll occasionally highlight other great businesses around Merthyr, Tredegar, Pontypridd, and beyond.

#### Locally Built, Locally Connected

We're proud to be based in Merthyr Tydfil, working with clients across South Wales — including [Cardiff](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cardiff), [Ebbw Vale](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ebbw_Vale), [Pontypridd](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pontypridd), and [Caerphilly](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Caerphilly). We're not a faceless agency. We're part of the local economy — and social media helps us stay closer to it.

#### Want to Build Your Own Online Presence?

We're helping businesses just like yours set up proper websites — clean, mobile-friendly, and SEO-ready. Our 5-page starter sites are perfect for trades and small businesses, and we offer maintenance if you want long-term support.

[Get a free website plan](/free-website-plan)

